'''Letta Mbulu''' (mofumahali ya [[African-American Soul]]) moepedi wa Jazz wa [[Aforika Borwa]] go simolla ka ngwaga wa 1960. O nyetseo ke [[Caiphus Semenya]] le yena ke moepedi wa Afrika Borwa ba kopane mo tlhahiso so [[King Kong]]<ref>http://southafrica.co.za/letta-mbulu.html</ref><ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letta_Mbulu</ref>. 

== Biography ==
O tsoaloa le ho holisoa ko [[Soweto]], [[Aforika Borwa|Afrika Borwa]] ka selemo sa 23 Phato 1942. O lilemo di li 77 <ref>https://www.sahistory.org.za/people/letta-mbulu</ref>. 

Letta Mbulu o qadile ho bina ho tloha ka selemo sa di 1960s. Ka nako ea bohlankana ba hae o khahloa hohle ba Afrika Borwa le [[England]] le tlhahiso sa [[King Kong]]  selemo sa 1965 o ile [[United States of America|United States Of America]] ka lebaka la [[Apartheid]] ka nako eo.

Ko [[New York City]] o kopane le libini tse ling ho tshwana le [[Miriam Makeba]], [[Hugh Masekela]] le [[Jones Gwangwa]] ho bua tse mmalwa. O ile ho bina ko di lihlahisoa go tshwana le Roots moo a amohetseng [[Emmy Award]] <ref>http://southafrica.co.za/letta-mbulu.html</ref>, [[The Color Purple]] (1985) le filimi [[A Warm December]] (1973) hape e ne le moeti mo Season sa botshelela sa [[Soul Train]]. Mbulu o sebelisana le [[Michael Jackson]] mo mino wa hahe [[Liberian Girl]]<ref>http://southafrica.co.za/letta-mbulu.html</ref>. 

Letta ke setho se ho qala [[The South African Artists United]] (SAAU) ka selemo sa 1986<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letta_Mbulu</ref>.
